Package ca.projectTOMi.tomi.viewModel

Provides classes for holding data that will not be persisted to the database.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BillableHoursReportExcelView
    Creates an excel representation of the BillableHoursReport.
    BillableHoursReportLine
    A single line from a Report to quickly analyse projects based on time spent on billable tasks.
    BudgetReport
    A Report that contains information regarding a projects budget.
    DataDumpReportExcelView
    Creates an excel representation of the DataDumpReport.
    DataDumpReportLine
    A model class for holding a single line from a data dump report.
    ProductivityReportExcelView
    Creates an excel representation of the ProductivityReport.
    ProductivityReportLine
    The class represents a single line of a bigger productivity report.
    ProjectViewModel
    Provides a means to reference a Project without most of the information required for a project.
